  <brief_title>Chronic Shoulder Pain Treated by Pressures With the Thumbs on the Trigger Points</brief_title>
  <official_title>Chronic Shoulder Pain of Myofascial Origin,a Randomised Clinical Trial Using Ischemic Compression Therapy.</official_title>
